{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894438854,"sessionID":"ses_2847266b0ffecWMsMka6mCOPeA","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8e9989001lAfpOy9k3ZGrAR","messageID":"msg_d7b8e66a4001ptC7BL9LRmqjrt","sessionID":"ses_2847266b0ffecWMsMka6mCOPeA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","offset":100,"limit":150},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n100: \n101: ### Invoke Command Flow\n102: \n103: ```\n104: invoke(workspace, payload, headers, provider)\n105:     │\n106:     ▼\n107: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n108: │ Parse Payload               │\n109: │ - Validate JSON format      │\n110: │ - Exit code 1 if invalid    │\n111: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n112:               │\n113:               ▼\n114: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n115: │ Parse Headers               │\n116: │ - Validate key:value format │\n117: │ - Exit code 1 if invalid    │\n118: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n119:               │\n120:               ▼\n121: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n122: │ Load Metadata               │\n123: │ - Read agent_metadata.yaml  │\n124: │ - Check agent_id exists     │\n125: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n126:               │\n127:               ▼\n128: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n129: │ Validate Prerequisites      │\n130: │ - Workspace exists          │\n131: │ - agent_endpoint present    │\n132: │ - k8s_deployment info       │\n133: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n134:               │\n135:               ├─ agentcube ─────► Build AgentRuntime URL\n136:               │                   - {router}/v1/namespaces/{ns}/\n137:               │                     agent-runtimes/{name}/invocations/\n138:               │                   - Add session header\n139:               │\n140:               └─ k8s ───────────► Use agent_endpoint directly\n141:                                   - Direct HTTP POST\n142:               │\n143:               ▼\n144: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n145: │ Execute HTTP Request        │\n146: │ - POST with payload         │\n147: │ - Include custom headers    │\n148: │ - Add session header (CR)   │\n149: │ - Handle timeouts           │\n150: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n151:               │\n152:               ▼\n153: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n154: │ Process Response            │\n155: │ - Parse JSON response       │\n156: │ - Display formatted result  │\n157: │ - Update metadata (CR)      │\n158: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n159:               │\n160:               ▼\n161:          Return Result\n162: ```\n163: \n164: ### Status Command Flow\n165: \n166: ```\n167: status(workspace, provider)\n168:     │\n169:     ▼\n170: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n171: │ Load Metadata               │\n172: │ - Read agent_metadata.yaml  │\n173: │ - Check agent_id exists     │\n174: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n175:               │\n176:               ▼\n177: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n178: │ Check Published State       │\n179: │ - If no agent_id:           │\n180: │   → \"not_published\"         │\n181: │   → Exit code 1             │\n182: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n183:               │\n184:               ├─ agentcube ─────► Query AgentRuntime CR\n185:               │                   - get_agent_runtime()\n186:               │                   - Extract status field\n187:               │                   - Check agentEndpoint\n188:               │\n189:               └─ k8s ───────────► Query K8s Deployment/Service\n190:                                   - get_agent_status()\n191:                                   - Check ready replicas\n192:                                   - Get service info\n193:               │\n194:               ▼\n195: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n196: │ Build Status Table          │\n197: │ - Rich Table formatting     │\n198: │ - Color-coded status        │\n199: │ - Deployment details        │\n200: └─────────────┬───────────────┘\n201:               │\n202:               ▼\n203: ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n204: │ Handle Status Result        │\n205: │ - \"ready\": success (exit 0) │\n206: │ - \"error\": exit 1           │\n207: │ - \"not_found\": exit 1       │\n208: │ - \"not_published\": exit 1   │\n209: └─────────────────────────────┘\n210: ```\n211: \n212: ### InvokeRuntime Class Structure\n213: \n214: ```python\n215: class InvokeRuntime:\n216:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n217:     \"\"\"Initialize with provider selection.\"\"\"\n218: \n219:     def invoke(\n220:         self,\n221:         workspace_path: Path,\n222:         payload: Dict[str, Any],\n223:         headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n224:     ) -> Any: ...\n225:     \"\"\"Main entry point for agent invocation.\"\"\"\n226: \n227:     def _validate_invoke_prerequisites(\n228:         self, workspace_path: Path\n229:     ) -> Tuple[AgentMetadata, str, str]: ...\n230:     \"\"\"Validate workspace and extract endpoint info.\"\"\"\n231: \n232:     async def _invoke_agent_via_agentcube(\n233:         self,\n234:         agent_id: str,\n235:         payload: Dict[str, Any],\n236:         headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]],\n237:         endpoint: str,\n238:         workspace_path: Path,\n239:     ) -> Any: ...\n240:     \"\"\"Invoke via AgentRuntime CR with session management.\"\"\"\n241: \n242:     async def _direct_http_invocation(\n243:         self,\n244:         endpoint: str,\n245:         payload: Dict[str, Any],\n246:         headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]],\n247:         workspace_path: Path,\n248:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n249:     \"\"\"Direct HTTP invocation for K8s deployments.\"\"\"\n\n(Showing lines 100-249 of 739. Use offset=250 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n### Invoke Command Flow\n\n```\ninvoke(workspace, payload, headers, provider)\n    │\n    ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────┐\n│ Parse Payload               │\n│ - Validate JSON format      │\n│ - Exit code 1 if invalid    │\n└─────────────┬───────────────┘\n              │\n              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────┐\n│ Parse Headers               │\n│ - Validate key:value format │\n│ - Exit code 1 if invalid    │\n└─────────────┬───────────────┘\n              │","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775894438842,"end":1775894438853}}}}
