{"type":"text","timestamp":1775894662863,"sessionID":"ses_2847266b0ffecWMsMka6mCOPeA","part":{"id":"prt_d7b91dc53001AZCUXz7zAvNYVu","messageID":"msg_d7b91c611001WOHNEC42bEmOKR","sessionID":"ses_2847266b0ffecWMsMka6mCOPeA","type":"text","text":"I've successfully written the `proposal.md` file for AR-024 — DockerService 封装. The proposal includes:\n\n## Summary of Contents\n\n### Header Information\n- **AR-024 — DockerService 封装**\n- Module: `cmd/cli`\n- Language: Python\n- Size: M (Medium)\n- Status: Proposed\n\n### Main Sections\n\n1. **Purpose** — Defines the DockerService as a unified interface for Docker operations within the AgentCube CLI\n\n2. **Scope** — Clearly defines:\n   - **In Scope**: Core Docker operations (build, tag, push, info, list), credential extraction, error handling\n   - **Out of Scope**: Docker Compose, volumes, networks, container runtime, registry management\n\n3. **Design** — Includes:\n   - Complete class structure with method signatures\n   - Build image flow diagram\n   - Push image flow diagram\n   - Credential extraction flow diagram\n\n4. **Impact Analysis** — Documents:\n   - Affected components (BuildRuntime, PublishRuntime)\n   - Data format changes for build/push results\n   - Error scenarios and exception types\n\n5. **Alternatives Considered** — Evaluates 5 alternatives:\n   - Direct SDK usage (Rejected)\n   - Subprocess-based CLI (Rejected)\n   - Async client (Partially Accepted)\n   - Podman compatibility (Deferred)\n   - External build service (Rejected)\n\n6. **Verification** — Provides code examples for:\n   - Docker availability check\n   - Image building (basic and with proxy args)\n   - Image tagging\n   - Image information retrieval\n   - Registry push with authentication\n   - Credential extraction from URLs\n   - Error handling\n\n7. **References** — Links to related specs and ARs\n\n8. **Success Criteria** — 25 specific, verifiable criteria covering all functionality\n\nThe file has been saved to `/home/dsj/benchmark